	<!-- Start each page with a <pb> formatted as above -->

<lb/><p>We are not in immediate 
<lb/>want of anything except
<lb/>the <term type="foodstuff">spices</term> but I send this
<lb/>order that if you have
<lb/>occasion to send other
<lb/>things up the country
<lb/>you may send these too
<lb/>Don't send them specially
<lb/>If you have <term type="foodstuff">dried <term type="people">American</term>
<lb/>apples</term> or <term type="foodstuff">peaches</term> send a 
<lb/>box, also some <term type="foodstuff">raisins</term>
<lb/>but there is no hurry
<lb/>for them - I have sent
<lb/>s packet of letters for 
<lb/>the <term type="occupation">Admiral</term> to your
<lb/>care. Also a number</p>
    
<lb/><cb rend="vertical"/><ab>I shall write you when we come
<lb/>down the <placeName><geogName type="river">Shire</geogName></placeName> to <placeName><settlement type="village">Shupanga</settlement></placeName></ab>
    
    <pb facs="liv_002694_0002.jpg" n="0002"/>
<lb/><p>of sketches for our Government
<lb/>in a box. Please do what
<lb/>you think best if you
<lb/>can forward them to
<lb/>a safe person at <placeName><country><w>Mosam<supplied>-</supplied>
<lb break="no"/>-bique</w></country></placeName> or write there desiring
<lb/>a ship to call &amp; send in
<lb/>a boat to <placeName><settlement type="village"><choice><orig>Kilimane</orig><reg>Quilimane</reg></choice></settlement></placeName>, do
<lb/>what you think will be
<lb/>the best for forwarding
<lb/>them to their destination
<lb/>I could not write you
<lb/>last night as the man
<lb/>was waiting till I sealed
<lb/>them up.</p> <closer>I am ever yours
<lb/>affectionately
<lb/><signed><persName>David Livingstone</persName></signed>
    
    <pb facs="liv_002694_0003.jpg" n="0003"/>
<lb/><hi rend="underline">Order for Goods</hi>
<lb/><hi rend="double-underline">At your convenience</hi>
<lb/>One bag of best <term type="foodstuff">coffee</term>
<lb/>A <!-- I cannot make out what this symbol is. JM --> of <term type="plant_foodstuff">mixed spices</term>
<lb/>to flavour our food or
<lb/>in want of that these
<lb/><term type="plant_foodstuff">Allspice</term> <choice><orig>1/2</orig><reg>1/2</reg></choice> <choice><abbr>lb</abbr><expan>pound</expan></choice>
<lb/><term type="plant_foodstuff">Cloves</term> <choice><orig>1/2</orig><reg>1/2</reg></choice> <choice><abbr>lb</abbr><expan>pound</expan></choice>
<lb/><term type="plant_foodstuff">Nutmegs</term> <choice><orig>1/2</orig><reg>1/2</reg></choice> a dozen
<lb/>and a fine wine
<lb/>sieve if you have
<lb/>such things at <placeName><settlement type="village">Quilimane</settlement></placeName>
<lb/>to sift <term type="foodstuff">flour</term>
<lb/><placeName><country><choice><orig>Mosambique</orig><reg>Mozambique</reg></choice></country></placeName> <term type="foodstuff">coffee</term> will
<lb/>do if you have us <placeName><geogName type="island">Zanzibar</geogName></placeName>
<lb/>or <term type="foodstuff">Mocha coffee</term></closer>  
    
    
